Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.60,0:13:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.08,0:13:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的不去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.77,0:13:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,現在還來得及…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.04,0:13:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你說什麼呢 快去吧 要趕不上巴士了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.92,0:13:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.31,0:13:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那就拜託你看家了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.31,0:13:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,素晴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.82,0:13:25.20,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,0)\an2\fn@FZLanTingHei-B-GBK\b0\frz285.8\pos(1122.4,248)\frx4\fry4\3c&H4E4C4C&}觀光巴士連環追尾事故
